      <a href="/fill" class="bg-emerald-600 px-3 py-2 rounded text-sm hover:bg-emerald-500">Wype≈Çnij okienka</a>
      <a href="/logout" class="bg-slate-700 px-3 py-2 rounded text-sm">Wyloguj</a>
