        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-700/60 bg-slate-950/60 p-3">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-sm">Usu≈Ñ wszystkie wpisy u≈ºytkownika</h3>
          <form id="del-all-form" class="flex items-center flex-wrap gap-2">
